Job Description
Tyco Fire & Security UAE, the regionâs leading provider of Fire Protection, Detection, Security and Telecommunications Systems, has openings for key positions to support the continued growth and development of our business in the UAE.
The positions will require candidates who have an outstanding knowledge of their fields, will be able to work on their own initiative, produce professional work to tight schedules and have the ability to present technical solutions to the blue chip clients.
ESTIMATION ENGINEERS (ELECTRICAL) - 4 Nos.
Graduate Electrical and Electronics or Instrumentation Engineers with hands-on experience in the design and estimation of Fire Detection Systems, Fire & Gas and other ELV systems, and 3-4 years of experience in a reputed company.
Conversant with NFPA, BS5839, EN54 and IEC61508 requirements.
Ideal candidates should be familiar with the use of CAD softwares. Experience in the GCC/ Middle East will be an added advantage along with a valid driving licence.Apply Instructions for This Job
